description.value: Welcome to this beautifully remodeled home located in the heart of Haddington, West Philadelphia. This delightful property offers a perfect blend of modern amenities and comfortable living, making it an ideal home for just about anyone! The heart of this home is its cozy living room, anchored by a built-on fireplace. This warm and inviting space is perfect for relaxing evenings or entertaining guests. Large windows flood the room with natural light, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. Enjoy the convenience of a dedicated laundry and powder room on the main level, designed for efficiency and ease of use. The powder room can also be closed off from the laundry room with a gorgeous barnyard door! Schedule your appointment to see this beauty today!

description.value: 3 bedroom 1.5 bath row home.. This home gives style, it gives character, affordability.. Just what you were looking for?.. Basement and small rear yard.. I must say it's worth scheduling a showing. Depending on your real estate needs this could be exactly what you were looking for.
